line_1: The bold example of thy loose amours,
line_2: Prevail'd on numbers of the heav'nly pow'rs;

line_1: Unmov'd she stands, slights all their soft Amours,
line_2: To gain this Fair who still her Heart secures,

line_1: Unmov'd she stands, slights all their soft Amours,
line_2: What would you give the Scene of Love were yours?

line_1: None like this Daemon of Amours.
Yet know, Base Man, I scorn your lewd Amours,
line_2: Hate them from all, not only cause they're yours.
